data.description: Lovely 1 story, 3 Beds 2 Baths. located in the beautiful neighborhood The Hammocks. This Townhouse model has a great floor plan with a lot of sunlight, a kitchen with good conditions appliance, formal dining, and a living room that you can enjoy with your family. Oversized, lot of parking spaces. It is already set in a prime location in South Florida, Malls, outlet shopping, restaurants, and more.
